<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.10">
<l>yāṉu mētti yēḻulaku muṟṟu mētti piṉṉaiyum</l>
<l>tāṉu mētti luntaṉṉai yētta vētta veṅkeytum</l>
<l>tēṉum pāluṅ kaṉṉalu mamutumākit tittippa</l>
<l>yāṉu mempi rāṉaiyē yētti ṉēṉyā ṉuyvāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I praise and the whole world praises and furthermore,</l>
<l>even though he himself praises while [they?] praise [and] praise him, where does that lead?</l>
<l>While being sweet like honey, milk, sugarcane and ambrosia</l>
<l>I to praised our lord in order to me to escape.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
